import React from 'react';
import logo from './logo.svg';
import './App.css';


function App() {
  return (
    <Form className="manualContainer" onSubmit={(e) => this.handleSubmit(e)}>
          <Group as={Col}>
              <label>First Name</label>
              <Control required onChange={(event) => {this.setState({firstName: event.target.value})}} placeholder="First Name" />
          </Group>
          <Group as={Col} >
              <label>Last Name</label>
              <Control required onChange={(event) => {this.setState({lastName: event.target.value})}} placeholder="Last Name" />
          </Group>
          <Group as={Col}>
              <label>Email</label>
              <Control required input onChange={(event) => {this.setState({email: event.target.value})}} type="email" placeholder="Enter Email" />
          </Group>
          <Group as={Col} controlId="formGridPhone">
              <label>Phone</label>
              <Control required onChange={(event) => {this.setState({phone: event.target.value})}} placeholder="Enter Phone Number" />
          </Group>
      <Group controlId="formGridAddress1">
          <label>Address</label>
          <Control required onChange={(event) => {this.setState({address: event.target.value})}} placeholder="1234 Main St" />
      </Group>
      <Group controlId="formGridAddress2">
          <label>Address 2</label>
          <Control onChange={(event) => {this.setState({address2: event.target.value})}}placeholder="Apartment, studio, or floor" />
      </Group>
          <Group as={Col} controlId="formGridCity">
              <label>City</label>
              <Control required onChange={(event) => {this.setState({city: event.target.value})}} placeholder="New York City"/>
          </Group>

          <Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
              <label>State</label>
              <Control required onChange={(event) => {this.setState({state: event.target.value})}} placeholder="New York"/>
          </Group>

          <Group as={Col} controlId="formGridZip">
              <label>Zip</label>
              <Control required onChange={(event) => {this.setState({zip: event.target.value})}}placeholder="10001"/>
          </Group>
          <Group as={Col} controlId="formGridOnlineProfile1">
              <label>Online Profile 1</label>
              <Control onChange={(event) => {this.setState({onlineProfile1: event.target.value})}} placeholder="Ex: LinkedIn"/>
          </Group>

          <Group as={Col} controlId="formGridOnlineProfile2">
              <label>Online Profile 2</label>
              <Control onChange={(event) => {this.setState({onlineProfile2: event.target.value})}} placeholder="Ex: GitHub"/>
          </Group>

          <Group as={Col} controlId="formGridOnlineProfile3">
              <label>Online Profile 3</label>
              <Control onChange={(event) => {this.setState({onlineProfile3: event.target.value})}} placeholder="Ex: Portfolio"/>
          </Group>
          <Group controlId="FormControlShortBio">
              <label>Short Bio</label>
          </Group>
          <Group controlId="FormControlHearProgram">
              <label>How did you hear about our program?</label>
              <Control required onChange={(event) => {this.setState({hearAboutProgram: event.target.value})}}as="select">
                  <placeholder>Select</placeholder>
                  <option>LinkedIn</option>
                  <option>Facebook</option>
                  <option>Google</option>
                  <option>Twitter</option>
                  <option>Facebook</option>
                  <option>Veterans Affaris</option>
                  <option>Operation Code</option>
                  <option>Hiring Heroes</option>
                  <option>IVMF</option>
                  <option>Friend/Family</option>
                  <option>Warrior Scholar</option>
                  <option>Course Report</option>
                  <option>GirHub</option>
                  <option>Reddit</option>
                  <option>Article</option>
                  <option>Other</option>
              </Control>
          </Group>
          <Group required controlId="FormControlCohort">
              <label>Which cohort are you applying to?</label>
              <Control required as="select" >
                  <option aria-label="option 0" label="Select"></option>
                  <option onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ cohortMarToAug: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 1" label="March 2 - August 7 2019"/> 
                  <option onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ cohortSeptToFeb: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 2" label="September 1 - February 26 2019"/>  
              </Control>
          </Group>
          <Group controlId="FormControlHowAttend">
              <label>How would you like to attend?</label>
                  <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ howAttendVirtual: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 1" label="Virtual"/> 
                  <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ howAttendInperson: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 2" label="In-Person (Syosset, NY)"/> 
          </Group>
          <Group controlId="FormControlCohort">
              <label>What is your highest education level?</label>
              <Control required onChange={(event) => {this.setState({highestEDU: event.target.value})}} as="select">
                  <option>High School</option>
                  <option>Associate Degree</option>
                  <option>Bacherlors Degree</option>
                  <option>Masters</option>
                  <option>Doctorate</option>
              </Control>
          </Group>
          <Group controlId="formGridOnlineProfile3">
              <label>List any other education not included above:</label>
              <Control onChange={(event) => {this.setState({eduNotIncluded: event.target.value})}} placeholder="Certifications, self-learning, etc.."/>
          </Group>
          <Group controlId="FormControlCohort">
              <label>Which of the following do you identify with (select all that apply)?</label>
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyCaucasian: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 1" label="Caucasian"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyAfricanAmerican: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 2" label="African American"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyHispanicLatin: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 3" label="Hispanic or Latin Origin"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyAsian: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 7" label="Asian"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyNativeAmerican: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 4" label="Native American"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyNativeHawaiianPacificIslander: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Native Hawaiian or Other Pacific Islander"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyMiddleEastNorthaAfrican: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Middle Eastern or North African"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyFemale: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Female"/>
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyMale: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Male"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyNonbinary: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Nonbinary"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyLgbtqiap: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="LGBTQIA+"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({  identifyOther: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Other"/> 
          </Group>
          <Group required controlId="formGridOnlineProfile3">
              <label>What are your primary intentions for enrolling in this program?</label>
              <Control required onChange={(e) => this.handleIntentionsChange(e)} as="select">
                  <option aria-label="option 0" label="Select"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 1" label="I intend to start a new lob within 180 days of graduating the program."/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 2" label="I intend to start a business or become a self-employed contractor upon graduation."/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 3" label="I intend to remain with my current employer upon graduation."/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 4" label="I am attending the program to learn new skills for self-enrichment and do not intent to pursue a job upon graduation."/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 5" label="I am attending the program in preparation to enroll in an accredited post-secondary institution and do not intend to pursue a job upon graduation."/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 6" label="Other"/> 
              </Control>
          </Group>
          <Group controlId="formGridOnlineProfile3">
              <label>Do you have coding experience?</label>
              <Control required onChange={(e) => this.handleCodingXPChange(e)} as="select">
                  <option aria-label="option 0" label="Select"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 1" label="None"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 2" label="Beginner (100 hours or less of tutorials)"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 3" label="Intermediate (Three or fewer classes and personal projects)"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 4" label="Advanced (Degree or professional experience)"/> 
              </Control>
          </Group> 
          <Group controlId="formGridOnlineProfile3">
              <label>Are you interested in any of the following scholarships?</label>
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipVeteran: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 1" label="Veteran In Person"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipWomenReEntry: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 2" label="Women re-entering the workforce"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipHispanicLatin: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 3" label="Hispanic or Latin Origin"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipAsian: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 7" label="Asian"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipNativeAmerican: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 4" label="Native American"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipNativeHawaiianPacificIslander: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Native Hawaiian or Other Pacific Islander"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipMiddleEastNorthaAfrican: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Middle Eastern or North African"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipFemale: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Female"/>
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipMale: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Male"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipNonbinary: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Nonbinary"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipLGBTQIAP: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="LGBTQIA+"/> 
              <Check onChange={(event) => {this.setState({ scholarshipOther: event.target.value })}} aria-label="option 5" label="Other"/> 
          </Group>
          <Group controlId="formGridOnlineProfile3">
              <label>If you are a VET do you intend to use the VET TEC program to pay for tuition and housing?</label>
              <Control required onChange={(e) => this.handleVETTECChange(e)} as="select">
                  <option aria-label="option 0" label="Select"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 2" label="Yes"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 3" label="No"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 0" label="I am not a veteran"/> 
              </Control>
          </Group>
          <Group controlId="formGridOnlineProfile3">
              <label>If you are a VET do you have GI BILL benefits you would like to use?</label>
              <Control required onChange={(e) => this.handleGIChange(e)} as="select">
                  <option aria-label="option 0" label="Select"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 2" label="Yes"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 3" label="No"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 0" label="I am not a veteran"/> 
              </Control>
          </Group>
          <Group controlId="formGridOnlineProfile3">
              <label>Are you currently authorized to work in the US?</label>
              <Control required as="select" onChange={(e) => this.handleAuthChange(e)}>
                  <option aria-label="option 0" label="Select"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 1" label="Yes"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 2"  label="No"/> 
              </Control>
          </Group> 
          <Group controlId="formGridOnlineProfile3">
              <label>Are you a US citizen or permanent resident?</label>
              <Control required as="select" onChange={(e) => this.handleResChange(e)}>
                  <option aria-label="option 0" label="Select"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 1" label="Yes"/> 
                  <option aria-label="option 2" label="No"/> 
              </Control>
          </Group>
          <Group required  controlId="formGridOnlineProfile3">
              <label>I am atleast 18 years old and I have at least a HS diploma or equivalent. I understand I will be asked to provide proof of my prior educational history if I enroll.</label>
                  <Control onChange={() => {this.setState({acknowledgement: 'acknowledged'})}} required as="select">
                      <option aria-label="option 0" label="Select"/> 
                      <option aria-label="option 1" label="I Acknowledge"/> 
                  </Control>
          </Group> 
      <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
          Submit
      </Button>
  </Form>
  );
}

export default App;
